WEBVTT

00:04.586 --> 00:07.371
Many know the legend of Kratos,...

00:07.653 --> 00:12.159
...the mortal turned god who brought down the very walls of Olympus.

00:12.995 --> 00:19.815
But there was a time before Kratos became the monster known as the Ghost of Sparta,...

00:20.948 --> 00:25.467
...a time when something other than rage consumed him,...

00:25.873 --> 00:28.868
...a time when in spite of the madness that plagued him,...

00:29.441 --> 00:33.365
...Kratos would break his blood oath to an unjust god,...

00:40.889 --> 00:45.800
...a time when he would no longer be bound in blood.

00:58.464 --> 01:02.100
